text: Glippets seems to have either short bodies and long tails or no tails
reesle's don't have wings. sometimes they have a small head, sometimes wide head
Morseth have either wide heads and slightly curved legs or straight legs with wings.
Daith if purple must have long body and tail. If orange, just needs long body or tail.
Zurp have long bodies; tails are irrelevant.
Yellow and fat no whiskers, yellow and skinny whiskers. Or green and skinny no whiskers or green and fat.
ackle; green and tall needs tail, blue and tall no tail, blue and short both tail and no tail.
zoov - any fat orange fish or any skinny fish w/o whiskers.
stup: wide head ans straight legs or small head and curved legs
crullet = no side spikes unless big and purple
